s that somebody would be held responsible are less than 3%.</p>\n<p>The 2025 clearance rate for Chicago shows that only in 24% of homicides there was a suspect charged with a crime. At the same time black juries have only a 12% conviction rate against black defendants.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://heyjackass.com/2025-homicide-clearance-rate/\" target=\"_blank\">https://heyjackass.com/2025-homicide-clearance-rate/</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://nitter.net/wallstreetapes/status/1960570206281195669\" target=\"_blank\">https://nitter.net/wallstreetapes/status/1960570206281195669</a></p>\n<p>That works out to a chance of only 2.88% for a conviction. Of course, that is assuming that the police did their work perfectly and charged the right person for the crime.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 11, "score_up": 88, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2048876810692096279", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaScJGx", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 771, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8585627, "raw_content": "", "author": "I-am-Orlando", "created": 1777331374041, "profile_picture": "TEnkk5XkT6JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "2025WhatIsTrue", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaScJGx.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/EricLDaugh/status/2048876810692096279?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Purple haired psycho Rep. Rosa DeLauro goe